{"type":"message","id":"ef48ecb7","parentId":"98655ef7","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:00:01.564Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:033adb0b-f08b-47e9-a0f6-a71bfe729a9d 每日 skill 升级检查] 执行每日 skill 升级检查。\n\n1. 运行 `clawhub list` 查看当前已装的 skill\n2. 运行 `clawhub update --all --no-input --force` 升级所有 skill\n3. 如果有 skill 升级失败，记下错误信息\n4. 汇报格式：\n   - 检查时间（Asia/Shanghai）\n   - 升级成功的 skill（列出版本号变化）\n   - 升级失败的 skill（列出错误）\n   - 已是最新、没动的 skill（仅列数量）\n5. 如果所有 skill 都已是最新，回复一句话即可，不要冗长\n\n注意：\n- 不要主动修改配置文件\n- 任何破坏性操作前先 stop 并汇报\nCurrent time: Friday, June 12th, 2026 - 04:00 (Asia/Shanghai)\nReference UTC: 2026-06-11 20:00 UTC\n\nUse the message tool if you need to notify the user directly for the current chat. If you do not send directly, your final plain-text reply will be delivered automatically."}],"timestamp":1781208001561}}
