{"type":"message","id":"4dc6c7e5","parentId":"17382939","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:01:49.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job for daily skill upgrade check. Let me read the clawhub skill first to understand how to use it, then execute the commands.\n","thinkingSignature":"8f17101486a8f7448a9a41eb04739b7e78e06f444d94c2ee5c46805269ea2971"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_676261d073f84ec38a8ef2d4","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49798,"output":72,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49870,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781208103256,"responseId":"067a47276a7d5ce537298617055368cc"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b65f32e","parentId":"4dc6c7e5","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:01:49.400Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_676261d073f84ec38a8ef2d4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: \"Search, install, update, sync, or publish agent skills with the ClawHub CLI and registry.\"\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1781208109399}}
{"type":"message","id":"15c60da2","parentId":"1b65f32e","timestamp":"2026-06-11T20:01:53.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand how to use clawhub. Let me run the two commands in sequence.\n","thinkingSignature":"1404bbb6fdf96ab1d2120b3455cba5d98ee4627163440eced4fa28ad7e99f7d3"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d70b3604240849359e54c917","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"clawhub list 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3050,"output":59,"cacheRead":47215,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50324,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781208109420,"responseId":"067a472e3f101c83864d1c70eb5ab198"}}
